asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Dr. Emmett Brown
description: Emmett Lathrop "Doc" Brown, Ph.D., is the inventor of the first time machine, built out of a 1981 DeLorean sports car. He possesses great admiration for scientists from previous eras, naming successive pet dogs Copernicus and Einstein, and having portraits of Isaac Newton, Benjamin Franklin, Thomas Edison and Albert Einstein in his laboratory. His favorite author is Jules Verne and his family name was originally "von Braun" before World War I. Emmett's work is highly regarded, having won a number of awards, however, he is quite absent-minded at times. Loud and sprightly, he often speaks with wide-eyed expressions and broad gestures  with "Great Scott!" being one of his well-known catchphrases. Doc has been involved with illegal and criminal enterprises (albeit as a means to obtain items for his inventions he could not purchase legally) but he is naive and care-free about the consequences of his actions. Doc and his good friend Marty actually met several years prior to the events of the first time travel experiment when Marty, out of curiosity, snuck into Doc's lab. The timeline of their friendship is of course confusing, and neither Doc nor Marty are certain of the true order of events.

name: Bobunny Ross
description:
Bobunny channeled his strong creative drive toward business and the deep appreciation of the artistic endeavors of others - especially Thingie-Majigs. 

He found those Fluffy Friends to be both helpful business partners and delightful distractions from the stresses he encountered at the markets and frequently attended the weekly salons held by the famous artist Leggy Bourgeois.

It was through the encouragement of his fellow artists at these salons that he finally found the courage to begin painting on his own. In an effort to learn and improve, he made video recordings of his landscape painting sessions. Originally subjected to light derision and mockery, these recordings are now legendary in Fluf World.

A friendly and popular fellow, Bobunny frequently travels to the icy north to party with the Bears in the Igloo Croo.

description:

Canelo.....Champion of Flufs.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
